<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Offer Letter</title>

    <style>
        body {
            font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #000;
            margin: 40px;
        }

        /* WATERMARK IMAGE */
        .watermark {
            position: fixed;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            width: 420px;
            opacity: 0.08;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%) rotate(-30deg);
            z-index: -1;
        }

        .center {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .bold {
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .spacer {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 40px;
            font-size: 12px;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <!-- STATIC WATERMARK -->
    <img src="http://localhost:3000/public/images/logo.png" class="watermark" />

    <p>Date: <%= joinedAt %>
    </p>

    <p>
        To,<br />
        <%= name %><br />
            Junagadh-362001
    </p>

    <p class="center bold">Offer Letter</p>

    <p>Dear <%= firstName %>,</p>

    <p>
        We are pleased an offer to you for a training opportunity at
        <strong>Techrover Solutions Training Center</strong>.
        We believe that your skills, talents, and potential will make a valuable
        contribution to our organization. This offer letter outlines the details
        of your training program, which is set to commence on Dt. <%= joinedAt %>.
    </p>

    <p>
        <strong>Training Program Overview:</strong>
        During your training (<%= duration %>), you will have the opportunity to
            gain hands-on experience and knowledge in <%= technology %>.
                Our program is designed to provide you with practical skills and insights
                to help you develop your career in this field.
    </p>

    <p><strong>Terms and Conditions:</strong></p>

    <p><strong>Attendance:</strong>
        You are expected to attend all training sessions, workshops, and meetings
        as required.
    </p>

    <p><strong>Confidentiality:</strong>
        You will be required to sign a confidentiality agreement to protect the
        company's proprietary information.
    </p>

    <p><strong>Evaluation:</strong>
        Your performance during the training program will be regularly reviewed
        to ensure your progress aligns with our training objectives.
    </p>

    <p><strong>Compensation:</strong>
        <%= compensation %>
    </p>

    <p><strong>Employment:</strong>
        This training program does not guarantee employment with Techrover Solutions
        Pvt. Ltd. Any potential employment opportunities will be discussed upon
        successful completion of the training.
    </p>

    <p>
        If you have any questions or need further information, please feel free to
        contact <%= contactPerson %> at Junagadh office.
    </p>

    <p>
        Congratulations on your selection for our training program. We believe it
        will be a mutually rewarding experience.
    </p>

    <div class="spacer"></div>

    <p>Sincerely,</p>

    <p>
        <strong>
            <%= signerName %>
        </strong><br />
        <%= signerDesignation %><br />
            Techrover Solutions
    </p>

    <p>
        B6, Milestone Complex,<br />
        Zanzarda Road, Junagadh<br />
        M. <%= signerMobile %>
    </p>

    <div class="footer">
        <p class="bold">Techrover Solutions</p>
        <p>
            406, Milestone Complex, Zanzarda Road, Junagadh, Gujarat-362001<br />
            [P] +91 9825997073 | [E] info@techroversolutions.com |
            [W] www.techroversolutions.com<br />
            CIN - U72900GJ2020OPC113964
        </p>
    </div>

</body>

</html>